    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-7-22.50, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH AUTHORIZES AN INCOME TAX CREDIT FOR EMPLOYERS WHO SPONSOR SKILLS TRAINING FOR EMPLOYEES, TO INCREASE THE MAXIMUM AGGREGATE AMOUNT OF TAX CREDITS THAT MAY BE CLAIMED BY ALL TAXPAYERS CLAIMING A CREDIT IN A TAXABLE YEAR; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
